<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11996] Add &quot;Table Creator&quot; to the HTD</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11996</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It will be nice storing the user who created the table. It is useful in situations where you want to remove a table but you don&apos;t know who asking to.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12741969">HBASE-11996</key>
            <summary>Add &quot;Table Creator&quot; to the HTD</summary>
